`CUSTOMER_OID`,
`CUSTOMER_ID`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_TYPE`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_LINE1`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_LINE2`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_CITY`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_DISTRICT`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_ZIP`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_STATE`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_ADDRESS_COUNTRY`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_PHONE_NO`,
`CUSTOMER_REG_PHONE_EXTEN`,
`CUSTOMER_COMM_ADDRESS_LINE1`,
`CUSTOMER_COMM_ADDRESS_LINE2`,
`CUSTOMER_COMM_ADDRESS_CITY`,
`CUSTOMER_COMM_ADDRESS_DISTRICT`,

(
	{{JSObject1.myFungenerateOIDfordetails()}},
		{{ appsmith.store.customerOID }},
		{{ appsmith.store.customerID }},
"Registered" ,{{vayFgnRegAddr1.text}},{{vayFgnRegAddr2.text}},{{vayFgnRegCity.text}},{{vayFgnRegDistrict.text}},{{vayFgnRegPostalCode.text}},{{vayFgnRegState.text}},{{vayFgnRegCountry.text}},{{appsmith.store.vayFGNRegPhonecopy}},{{vayFgnRegExtn.text}},{{vayFgnComAddr1.text}},{{vayFgnComAddr2.text}},{{vayFgnComCity.text}},{{vayFgnComDistrict.text}},{{vayFgnComPostalCode.text}},{{vayFgnComState.text}},{{vayFgnComCountry.text}},{{vayFgnComPhone.text}},{{vayFgnComExtn.text}});
